Actually, no one moded. Mosquitor opened the door when he hears someone 
beating on it, that's how the dinobots got in.

::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor groans, opening his eyes. He was dented and in terrible condition, 
as ussual. He nods when he recieves Black Arachnia's orders.

"As you wish, leadership!" he exclaims into his comm, limping off toward the 
new pod.
